HEADWORD: Sassarara
<hw>Sas`sa*ra"ra</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Perh. a
corruption of <ets>certiorari</ets>, the name of a writ.]</ety> <def>A
word used to emphasize a statement.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Out she shall pack, with a <qex>sassarara</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Goldsmith.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

